Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:06.04,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Ragna-mail connector, purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.91,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy pressure barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:13.15,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonium reactor, engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:16.49,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Connect D-brane resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.66,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Begin feeding all power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.02,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,The preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:26.96,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.55,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Ange isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.26,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.64,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.44,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need Ange?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:44.76,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I've promised you my loyalty, Embryo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:47.86,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I fought for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:51.36,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Yet it's Ange again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.56,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:01:01.29,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,It's strong, intelligent women \Nthat will create my new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.63,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:08.58,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I chose Ange for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.00,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for foolish women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.30,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Ange will surely come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:20.45,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,If only to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:26.60,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Salia, if you were truly \Nintelligent and strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.27,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you would know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.93,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll capture Ange and make her submit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:37.47,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping you do, my Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.00,Ange-top,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Replace the damaged plating on the laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.44,Ange-top,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Prioritize resupplying on Rosalie's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.37,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Do a damage check on Hilda's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.63,Ange-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.02,Ange-main,Nonna,0000,0000,0000,,Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.09,Ange-main,Nonna,0000,0000,0000,,Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.26,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Merge the two Earths?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.89,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,The Ragna-mails are the regulators,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.43,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Aura is the energy source.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:32.94,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo is going to merge the \Ntwo Earths, space-time and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.75,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,He'll make a new Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.33,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,She can't take anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.28,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:45.61,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,If the two Earths were to merge, \Neverything would be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.27,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:54.21,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, the People of Aura\Nwish for an alliance with the Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.50,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:04:00.92,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be difficult to penetrate Embryo's \Ndefenses with our Ryushinki alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.63,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine your situation is much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.63,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we can't do anything \Nagainst their Ragna-mails alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:13.66,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.73,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,We can form an alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.84,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,But only once Ange is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.49,Ange-announcer,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Ange isn't back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:33.21,Ange-announcer,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, oh dear, where has my wife gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.32,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.42,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.00,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.30,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.51,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Vulcan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.44,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.59,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,She's only being manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.48,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.14,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after a woman who left you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.31,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,That's pathetic, Sir Tuner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.58,Ange-announcer,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,The princess of the DRAGONs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.90,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.15,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Ange and I will be seeing you soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.60,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,To have your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.95,Ange-announcer,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.71,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.57,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.26,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Embryo is desperate to find Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:28.93,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Can you avoid his notice and rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.73,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Make no mistake, Ange will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.15,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.40,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.26,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, oh dear. What a barbaric woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.00,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.50,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ersha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.04,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,The preschool children...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:07.30,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Please, bring them back to life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.26,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:16.24,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,The new world is for my new humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.98,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,We can't bring those girls there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.41,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:27.98,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you be a mother to the \Nnew humanity of my new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.91,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you, Ersha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.92,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.08,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.53,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Those children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:42.00,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Those children are my everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.63,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.42,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.66,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a more intelligent woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.82,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Do not trouble me further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.41,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.62,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going to wait for Ange?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.39,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,The world's in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.59,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.83,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.29,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,You're only thinking about Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.40,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do without Ange and the Villkiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.44,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Chris took us down by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.55,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with the DRAGONs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:40.75,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything, if it means killing Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.39,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.98,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.94,Ange-main,Rollnya,0000,0000,0000,,For Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.98,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Rosalie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.60,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:57.69,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.16,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.00,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too stupid to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:10.07,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd always be friends with Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:14.84,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was Chris that \Nfelled the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.30,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.77,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,She shot down the Villkiss \Nand murdered a new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.23,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo's men are exemplary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.23,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers and the commander alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.22,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.14,Ange-main,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we'd been nicer to Salia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:38.23,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she might have never become an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.88,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:52.21,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,A peaceful world, a fair life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.47,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.06,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it was that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.67,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,When I went home, you were always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.76,Ange-internal/narrator,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,When I got home, Momoka, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.02,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.99,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge you, Alektra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.93,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,"Ange will surely come here."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.50,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm hoping you do, my Salia," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.09,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:22.72,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,But Ange, if you're gone,\Nand if he understands that I'm stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.98,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo-sama will accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.59,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,He'll accept my value.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.55,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,If I can achieve that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.27,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:47.29,Ange-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,The DRAGONs' voices interfere \Nwith Mana and drive humans mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:53.21,Ange-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,That's why only the Norma could fight them,\Nbecause they have no Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.80,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,I was never told about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.43,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,This world is full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:06.13,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,But Normas, who could destroy Mana,\Nwould expose all those lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:09.14,Ange-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they were oppressed and isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:15.25,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,The humans were programmed\Nto instinctively despise the Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.67,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then we're all just puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.57,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.95,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, the Light of Mana—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.71,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.89,Ange-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I'm calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.78,Ange-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.54,Ange-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I use my Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.08,Ange-main,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,So it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.84,Ange-main,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction and\Nrecreation of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:46.31,Ange-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,And in what manner are\Nwe to greet this new world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:51.39,Ange-main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,We must escape quickly, or we'll\Nbe caught in the space-time merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.98,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you'd be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.77,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,The new world will be\Nmade by intelligent women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:05.32,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,You failures will take responsibility \Nfor plunging this world into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.33,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.60,Ange-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Are you abandoning us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.30,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.02,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.26,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.35,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.22,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the First Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:36.65,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Queen Emperor Sylvia I!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.46,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Come help me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.21,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Ersha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.62,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.78,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.17,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.36,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.52,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.43,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Those children were all I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.52,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he manipulated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:11.97,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an empty, shallow whore\N with nothing left to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.79,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:22.44,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,With having to kill your friends? \NHilda-chan and Rosalie-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.54,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.67,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.49,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.58,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.80,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.98,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Morgan-san died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.37,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:07.23,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to fight Embryo was futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.59,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,As was trying to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.26,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.59,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go crazy from the loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.25,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,People aren't meant to live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.79,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:26.05,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,A girl washed up today, \Nalong with the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.84,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.80,Ange-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and she doesn't listen to \Nwhat anyone has to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.35,Ange-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ange is light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.14,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,She's light, shining in \Nfrom the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:44.32,Ange-internal/narrator,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Mom, I finally found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.72,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect her. That's my duty..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.03,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mine alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:56.39,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,He always protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.97,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.52,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:04.42,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.49,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.43,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.50,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.75,Ange-flashback,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,You need to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.68,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.33,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even die by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.33,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.12,Ange-flashback,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,You're even prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.40,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.54,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.76,Ange-flashback,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.80,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Were you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.79,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,With losing everything for your duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.92,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of world were you hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:48.15,Ange-flashback,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just hoping we'll\Nget to enjoy peace someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.66,Ange-flashback,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:59.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you're not here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.23,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:14.44,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew this would happen,\NI would've let him go all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.60,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.65,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.11,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:27.48,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Ange's knight is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.99,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.94,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.24,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.04,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of Embryo's illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.79,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.40,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't injured from the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.29,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have your gunshot wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.67,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:54.97,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.55,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.26,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.21,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.72,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.79,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:13.48,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Ange, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.86,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.24,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Find out? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.27,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:35.34,Ange-announcer,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me? Ersha here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.18,Ange-announcer,Olivier,0000,0000,0000,,A white bra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.22,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a white flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.91,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Ersha here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.10,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.73,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.40,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.52,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,A lot more than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.55,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.24,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:19:00.16,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,People aren't meant to live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.33,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,You read my journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.71,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything when you're alone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.37,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You can't insult each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.88,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.22,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You really weren't brought \Nback to life, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.34,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.44,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.43,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.21,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.78,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.74,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.\NEverything looks like it's brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:53.31,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That pervert stalker asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:57.69,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,...to destroy the world and make a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:02.03,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.49,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how incomplete and foolish it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.39,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.00,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.56,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.35,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.52,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:22.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.88,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.02,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,With the lives Momoka protected for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.95,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:36.39,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Today's menu is smoked river fish,\Nberry and mushroom potage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:40.84,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,brawn with crimson glory vine sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.29,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I highly recommend this potage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:45.22,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was left to stew for about twelve hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.52,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Twelve hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.64,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why's Momoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.85,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to this frying pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.24,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are my top maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.89,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.27,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.83,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use Mana anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.80,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:27.41,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Embryo's beginning the destruction \Nand recreation of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.20,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.06,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mom's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:38.86,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.43,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to retrieve the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.15,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that'll be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:49.01,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.89,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.09,next episode preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,519)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.55,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Ange!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:31.85,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You changed into flameproof clothing \Nat the exact instant the explosion happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:33.64,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a convenient plot twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.72,Ange-main,Tusk,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I'm a convenient person!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.98,Ange-NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(899,1)}The Warped World
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.79,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,You really were a ninja.
